I get this quite frequently also.  I think that the technicians facilitate
the communication with the Others.  In my experience, when I am doing a
session and I am asking questions, the Others kind of line-up to all be
heard at once.  Many times I have to ask them to only let one at a time
speak because a lot of chatter results.  I received these two clips while
ghosting on Saturday night and I think that they are directly pertinent to
this idea.

The first one you will hear is a child saying how many people are there to
speak through the box.

The second clip is a good one.  In this one you will hear my technician
reiterating my request to the Others.

Tim

